<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">
      ¿Listo para tu <span class="italic font-normal text-olive">mejor sonrisa</span>?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-muted text-base max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
      Agenda tu consulta hoy y descubre cómo podemos transformar tu salud dental con tecnología de punta y atención personalizada.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <button data-booking class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-terracotta text-white font-semibold rounded-full px-8 py-3.5 text-sm hover:bg-terracotta-dark transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        Agendar Cita
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <a href="#servicios" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-dark/20 text-dark font-semibold rounded-full px-8 py-3.5 text-sm hover:border-dark hover:bg-dark hover:text-white transition-all">
        Ver Servicios
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
